{"title":"博客的诞生","date":"2018-06-12T08:37:56.000Z","link":"post/博客的诞生","comments":true,"categories":["技术"],"updated":"2022-11-23T03:03:22.751Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><h1 id=\"简介\"><a href=\"#简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简介\"></a>简介</h1><p>一款完全属于自己的博客，所用技术：<code>nodeJs</code>，<code>git</code>，<code>hexo</code></p>\n<h1 id=\"hexo-本地配置\"><a href=\"#hexo-本地配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 本地配置\"></a>hexo 本地配置</h1><h2 id=\"安装-hexo\"><a href=\"#安装-hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 hexo\"></a>安装 hexo</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir hexo &amp;&amp; cd hexo</span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm i hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm i hexo --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"检测是否安装成功\"><a href=\"#检测是否安装成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检测是否安装成功\"></a>检测是否安装成功</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"初始化\"><a href=\"#初始化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化\"></a>初始化</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"安装依赖包\"><a href=\"#安装依赖包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装依赖包\"></a>安装依赖包</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm i</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"首次体验-hexo\"><a href=\"#首次体验-hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"首次体验 hexo\"></a>首次体验 hexo</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">清除冗余代码，必要时使用</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">编译</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">启动服务器</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p>此时在浏览器输入 <code>localhost:4000</code> 就可看到自己的博客啦</p>\n<h2 id=\"发布\"><a href=\"#发布\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"发布\"></a>发布</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">需提前安装一个扩展</span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm i hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">再发布</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p>此时在浏览器输入 <code>自己在 git 上设置的博客地址</code> 就可看到自己的博客啦</p>\n<h2 id=\"新建博客\"><a href=\"#新建博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建博客\"></a>新建博客</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new 博客名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"新建文件夹\"><a href=\"#新建文件夹\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建文件夹\"></a>新建文件夹</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page 博客名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"将-hexo-与-github-page-联系起来\"><a href=\"#将-hexo-与-github-page-联系起来\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将 hexo 与 github page 联系起来\"></a>将 hexo 与 github page 联系起来</h2><h3 id=\"配置-git-个人信息\"><a href=\"#配置-git-个人信息\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置 git 个人信息\"></a>配置 git 个人信息</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global urser.name \"zine-fj\"</span><br><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email \"747810974@qq.com\"</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">生成秘钥</span><br><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C \"747810974@qq.com\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"配置-Deployment\"><a href=\"#配置-Deployment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置 Deployment\"></a>配置 Deployment</h3><p>在hexo根目录中的 _config.yml，找到Deployment，然后操作如下:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: git@github.com:yourname/yourname.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"主题配置\"><a href=\"#主题配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主题配置\"></a>主题配置</h1><p>将所用到的主题下载到 <code>根文件</code> 里面的 <code>theme</code>中，然后在 <code>根文件</code> 的 <code>_config.yml</code> 中配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">theme: inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"主题推荐\"><a href=\"#主题推荐\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主题推荐\"></a>主题推荐</h1><ul>\n<li>最经典主题 <code>next</code>：<a href=\"https://notes.iissnan.com/\">next</a></li>\n<li>比较清新的一款主题 <code>Yilia</code>：<a href=\"http://litten.me/\">Yilia</a></li>\n<li>很像网页的一款主题 <code>skapp</code>：<a href=\"http://blog.minfive.com/\">skapp</a></li>\n<li>卡片化较多的一款主题 <code>matery</code>: <a href=\"https://blinkfox.github.io/\">matery</a><br>…  </li>\n<li>目前最看上眼的主题 <code>inside</code>: <a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/\">inside</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>","prev":{"title":"博客在不同电脑异步问题","link":"post/博客在不同电脑异步问题"},"plink":"https://zine-fj.github.io/blog/post/博客的诞生/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"简介","index":"1"},{"title":"","id":"hexo-本地配置","index":"2","children":[{"title":"","id":"安装-hexo","index":"2.1"},{"title":"","id":"检测是否安装成功","index":"2.2","children":[{"title":"","id":"初始化","index":"2.2.1"},{"title":"","id":"安装依赖包","index":"2.2.2"},{"title":"","id":"首次体验-hexo","index":"2.2.3"}]},{"title":"","id":"发布","index":"2.3"},{"title":"","id":"新建博客","index":"2.4"},{"title":"","id":"新建文件夹","index":"2.5"},{"title":"","id":"将-hexo-与-github-page-联系起来","index":"2.6","children":[{"title":"","id":"配置-git-个人信息","index":"2.6.1"},{"title":"","id":"配置-Deployment","index":"2.6.2"}]}]},{"title":"","id":"主题配置","index":"3"},{"title":"","id":"主题推荐","index":"4"}]}